name: Pondok Genyol Bu Agus Family Sading
address: Sading, Mengwi, Badung Regency, Bali 80115, Indonesia
review 1: Have been here a few times, never really disappointed with the Babi Genyol or Babi Guling with rice before, but the one I had yesterday was not so special. It didn't taste bad, but didn't really make me want to come back especially for the rice in the future. The portion seemed smaller as well. But I really liked the Bubur. Not so many condiments, but tasted good, will have this if I'm not too hungry when I'm in the area next time.
review 2: Over price and taste really bad (too sweet for all types)! Not worth at all, also need to improve the selling service.
review 3: Too sweet for my taste, sorry
review 4: good food and good place,  recommended
